Package: ibmsmooth
Type: Package
Title: Integrated Brownian Motion Smoothing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "Jessalyn", family = "Sebastian", email = "jessalys@uci.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits global and locally adaptive integrated Brownian motion smoothers
    for Gaussian observations using either Stan or INLA. Stan models support
    full MCMC inference with global and horseshoe-adaptive smoothness. INLA
    models provide a fast latent Gaussian implementation with optional
    B-spline adaptivity for the log precision function.
